19/11/2008
PRISTINA, Kosovo -- Greek Foreign Minister Dora Bakoyannis says that although Greece currently does not recognise Kosovo's independence, it should accept reality, according to media reports Wednesday (November 19th). 
In an interview with the Albanian TV channel Vizion Plus, Bakoyannis said Greece will recognise Kosovo's independence very soon but did not provide a date. 
(Koha Ditore - 19/11/08; Vizion + - 17/11/08)
